# --- Dependencies ---
# Matches node_modules in root, or any sub directory.
**/node_modules/
# Matches Python virtual environments (common names)
**/venv/
**/env/
**/__pycache__/
**/.venv/

# --- Environment & Secrets ---
# Matches .env, .env.local, .env.secret, etc., anywhere
**/.env
**/.env.*
# Private keys and certificates
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.pub
**/secrets.json

# --- Operating System Files ---
# Mac system files
**/.DS_Store
# Windows system files
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# --- IDE & Editor Folders ---
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.project
